trans-unit.source: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner provides design-time support for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner fornece suporte de tempo de design para <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>controles.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: It extends its parent class, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>, by adding a control-specific <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> collection.
trans-unit.target: Ele estende sua classe pai, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>, adicionando um controle específico <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>para o <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A>coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.TemplateGroups%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartDesigner>

trans-unit.source: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner does not render the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner não processa associado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>controle na superfície de design.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the parent method to prevent rendering of the control.
trans-unit.target: Substitui o método pai para evitar o processamento do controle.

trans-unit.source: If there is no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A> associated with the control, the designer displays the standard gray box with the class name and instance name of the control.
trans-unit.target: Se não houver nenhum <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A>associado ao controle, o designer exibe a caixa cinza padrão com o nome de classe e o nome da instância do controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart.WebPartsTemplate%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, no design-time rendering occurs at all because the check boxes and Web Parts titles are rendered by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome> instead of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> itself.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, nenhum processamento de tempo de design em todos os ocorre porque as caixas de seleção e títulos de Web Parts são renderizados pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome>em vez do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart>em si.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPartChrome>

trans-unit.source: Either an empty string ("") or the value of <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml*>.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia vazia ("") ou o valor de <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.DeclarativeCatalogPartDesigner.GetEmptyDesignTimeHtml*>

Uma cadeia de caracteres de marcação vazio.
